  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Collidable
    Interface that all things with collision detection implement
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Enemy
    Enemy Class that represents a single enemy unit in the game
    EnemyManager
    The EnemyManager Class represents all the enemies on the grid this class is intended to be used with a data structure using Rooms
    EnemyRoom
    This is a subclass of the Room class and represents a room full of enemies
    GameBoard
    This is the GameBoard Class the manages the Game "Legends of Kenjiro" as a whole by tying all the other classes together
    Main
    Main Class that initiates the Game "Legend of Kenjiro"
    Player
    Player class that represents the users character
    PlayerData
    Holds data for the player in the database
    Room
    Room class that represents a single room in the dungeon
    Weapon
    Weapon Class that represents a weapon a Player can use (In the Future Enemy Class may use it too)
